                        Palestinian State Ready in Near Future
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 21.09.2010]</p>
                <p>The international donor group in support of the Palestinians (AHLC) today reconfirmed its support for the Palestinian government program that aims to establish a Palestinian state by August 2011.  </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
        <hr class="seperator" />   
    
        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            
            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/ud/press/news/2010/coastal_states_africa.html?id=614650" title="">
                        Norway signs agreement with coastal states in Africa
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 21.09.2010]</p>
                <p>Minister of the Environment and International Development Erik Solheim will sign an agreement with six countries in Africa that will help them to gain jurisdiction over their own oil and gas resources. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
