        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            
            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/ud/press/news/2010/norway-redoubles-its-support-for-flood-v.html?id=614537" title="">
                        Norway redoubles its support for flood victims in Pakistan
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 19.09.2010]</p>
                <p>Norway has decided to increase its assistance for the flood victims in Pakistan to USD 66 million. The situation is critical, and the number of victims keeps rising. The floods are the worst ever in the history of Pakistan. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
