                    <a href="/en/dep/krd/press/press-releases/2010/norway-signs-cooperation-agreement-with-.html?id=614319" title="">
                        Norway signs cooperation agreement with India
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Ministry of Local Government and Regional Development, 15.09.2010]</p>
                <p>Today, Norway’s Minister of Local Government and Regional Development Liv Signe Navarsete and Indian minister Dr. C. P. Joshi signed a Memorandum of Understanding for mutual cooperation on local governance in the two countries.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
