                    <a href="/en/dep/ud/press/news/2010/killing_israeli.html?id=613325" title="">
                        Norway condemns killing of four Israeli citizens
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 01.09.2010]</p>
                <p>On Tuesday 31 August, four Israeli citizens were shot dead close to the Israeli settlement of Kiryat Arba on the West Bank. Hamas has taken responsibility for this outrage, which took place on the day before the start of negotiations between Israel and the Palestinians in Washington.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
